Team B has a brainstorming session to discuss about a product roadmap
Date: 09/13/24

Continue to update: Team Meeting - Sun 22 4pm

Epics:
  - Templates management
  - Files management
  - Documents Drafting (not quite sure about the epic name)
  - User management 
  - Log in/Sign up

Milestones: 
  - Discovery and System Design Base Setup
  - UI design for Templates management function
  - UI design for Files management function
  - UI design for Documents Drafting function
  - UI design for User management function
  - UI design for Log in/Sign up
  - Prototyping for all functions

Milestones & Issues:

1st Milestone: Discovery and System Design Base Setup
  #1 As a user, I want to see all main pages in header or left-side panel so that I can navigate easily in the system.
  #2 As a user, I want to see the first page of Templates management function so that I can view all templates and start working with them.
  #3 As a user, I want to see the first empty page of Files management function so that I can see all documents I have created.
  #4 As a user, I want to see the first page of Documents Drafting function so that I can start drafting a document with information.
  #5 As a user, I want to see the first page of User management function so that I can view all people (accounts) roles or access.
  #6 Set up a design system on Figma

2nd Milestone: UI design for Templates management function
  #1 As a user, I want to see the first page of Templates management function so that I can view all templates and start working with them. 
  #2 As a user, I want to be able upload a document that becomes a template.
  #3 As a user, I want to be able to select any number of templates to work on all at once.
  #4 As a user, I want to be able to categorize templates.
  #5 As a user, I want to be able to quickly find the template I want to use.
  #6 As a user, I want to be able to remove templates from my selection in case of accidents.
  #7 As a user, I want to be able to see a preview of what may be on a template that I forgot the contents of.
  #8 As a user, I want to be able to see what fields may be required for a template.
  #9 As a user, 

3rd Milestone: UI design for Files management function
  #1 As a user, I want to see the first empty page of the Files Management function so I can view all the documents I have created.
  #2 As a user, I want to upload documents to the system and see them listed in my Files Management dashboard. 
  #3 As a user, I want to be able to organize my documents into folders or categories for easy retrieval.
  #4 As a user, I want to have a search function so I can quickly find the documents I need.
  #5 As a user, I want to be able to download, rename, or delete files directly from the Files Management page.

4th Milestone: UI design for Documents Drafting function
  #1 As a user, I want some editable filds when starting a new document.
  #2 As a user, I want a template previes on real time in the middle of the screen.
  #3 As a user, I want a progress bar at the top of the screen, so I have an idea on how much porgress I have done and what do I have left
  #4 As a user, I want a common selected templates to save time to the user.
